<div id="outline-container-orgheadline36" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgheadline36"><span class="section-number-3">8.6</span> Summary</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-8-6">
<div class="xlarge">
<p>
Latplan: Latent-space Planner.
</p>

</div>

<div class="larger">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li><b>bridges <i>real-world</i> and <i>propositional</i> representations.</b></li>
<li><b>performs a <i>propositional, logical, sound reasoning</i>.</b></li>
<li><b>returns a <i>real-world</i> output</b> (e.g. images).</li>
<li><b>runs in a <i>completely automated, unsupervised</i> manner.</b></li>
</ul>

</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgheadline38" class="outline-2">
