<div id="outline-container-orgheadline49" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgheadline49"><span class="section-number-2">10</span> State AutoEncoder (SAE)</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-10">
<p>
SAE is a <b>neural network</b> which provides two functions:
</p>

<ul class="org-ul">
<li>$b = Encode(r)$: <b>maps a raw datum $r\;$to a bit vector $b\;$</b></li>

<li>$\tilde{r} = Decode(b)$: <b>maps a bit vector $b\;$to a raw datum $\tilde{r}$</b></li>
</ul>

<div class="larger">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li><b>A bidirectional mapping between</b>

<ul class="org-ul">
<li><b>subsymbolic representation</b> (image array) and</li>

<li><p>
<b>symbolic representation</b>
</p>

<div class="alignright">
<p>
(bit vectors = propositional variables)
</p>

</div></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>

</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgheadline39" class="outline-3">
