<div id="outline-container-orgheadline62" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgheadline62"><span class="section-number-2">12</span> AMA<sub>1</sub> Experiments</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-12">
<p>
SAE: <b>trained with 20k images</b> (note: &gt; 360k entire states in 8-puzzle)
</p>

<ul class="org-ul">
<li><b><i>SAE is generalizing</i></b></li>
</ul>

<p>
AMA<sub>1</sub>: requires the entire transistions (note: &gt; 1M transitions in 8-puzzle)
</p>

<ul class="org-ul">
<li><span class="underline"><i>AMA<sub>1</sub> is NOT generalizing, being an oracle</i></span></li>
</ul>

<p>
Planner: a State-of-the-Art, Fast Downward (Helmert, 08)
</p>

<ul class="org-ul">
<li>$A^*$<b>(optimal search)</b> : <b>It must find an optimal solution</b></li>

<li>Runtime: ~3sec (instances are too small for symbolic systems)</li>
</ul>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgheadline54" class="outline-3">
