<div id="outline-container-orgheadline93" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgheadline93"><span class="section-number-2">27</span> AMA<sub>2</sub> Experiments 2</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-27">
<div class="container-fluid">
<div class="row-fluid">
<div class="span6">
<p>
How accurate are Action Discriminators?
</p>

<p>
Measure the type-1 / type-2 error in %
</p>

